<h2>Accessibility</h2>
<p>This component supports WCAG 2.2 AA accessibility requirements. Easy Read is not a replacement for accessible HTML but should be provided in addition to standard content. Ensure that Easy Read files are accessible PDFs with correct reading order, alt text for images, and searchable text.</p>

